title: Something don't seem right
creator_credit: Australian Broadcasting Commission, Bill Steller and Robin Hughes
brief_description: One of a series of films which looks at the lives of children growing up in different environments. Shows the world of a child living in the inner city area, attending Newtown High School, and the physical and financial constraints on his family.
